Hey there

This map i created today. about 8 hours of buildtime, and 2 hours of compile time.
the map has got 18 spawnpoints, 9 on each side.

This knife arena is created by me and has custom textures, hdr lightning and automaticly opened gates ;).

I put an timer on the gates, so they open 2 sec out of 10 seconds.
so you have to be quick :)

map contains:
18 spawnpoints
hdr lightning
custom textures

have fun, and let me know if something is wrong

--hamster out
